    "causal_summary": "Packet 059 produced a stress-test methodology that surfaced two real design gaps in `@code` after a single round of failure-path scenarios — gaps that the pre-merge structural smoke test (CP-026) had missed entirely. The methodology is reusable: same-task A/B dispatch, sandboxed isolation, grep-only verdict signals, multi-round iterative edits with measurable score progression, and a smart-router audit asking \"does the skill *actually fire its routing logic*, or does the agent just read SKILL.md and stop?\"",
